and (ii) dense row-regular $\\{0,1\\}$-matrices, for\nwhich the previous best known bound is $O_{C}(n^{-C})$ for any constant $C>0$\ndue to Nguyen.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Apr 2019 17:05:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-24"}
