ls, we extend Friedman's theorem\non minimal models of analysis, and develop indicators for countable fragments\nof $\\mathcal L_{\\infty\\omega}$, with some representability results in\n$\\omega$-logic.\n  We close with an exposition of the Paris-Harrington statement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Apr 2019 21:15:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-25"}
